{"tid":1480112,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港818遊行促300萬人上街 全球30城市響應","createTime":"2019-08-17T07:20:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T05:44:52.000Z","uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c65c91aea62f68f4d586192a8dd00435ec37f085","tid":1480112,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:20:04.000Z","msg":"香港今明兩天有多場集會遊行，其中由民間人權陣線（民陣）發起、主題為「止黑爆、制警亂」的「818」遊行，明天下午2時登場，全球將有十個國家、逾30個城市響應。<br />\n<br />\n香港本周末進入反送中運動另一高峰。香港教育界中午走上街頭，要求港府立即回應民眾針對反送中所提出的五大訴求。由香港教育專業人員協會發起的這次遊行，主題為「守護下一代，為良知發聲」，上午11時在中環遮打花園集會後，遊行前往禮賓府。<br />\n<br />\n守護香港大聯盟則在今天傍晚於金鐘添馬公園舉行「反暴力、救香港」大集會，呼籲香港社會各界反對一切形式的暴力，儘快恢復社會正常秩序。<br />\n<br />\n但最讓港府與北京高度戒備的是明天的「818」大遊行。民陣原預計明天下午3時由銅鑼灣維多利亞公園出發，遊行至中環遮打道行人專用區，希望能號召300萬名港人上街，再創香港遊行人數新高。<br />\n<br />\n不過，香港警方已禁止民陣公眾遊行及在遮打道行人專用區集會，只批准民陣明日上午10時至晚上11時在維多利亞公園舉行集會。民陣就此提出上訴，但昨遭駁回，遊行仍不獲批准。<br />\n<br />\n對此，民陣表示考慮以司法覆核方式，捍衛人民集會自由。民陣同時呼籲港人，明天無論如何都要在下午2時進入維園。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/120538/3994434\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F120538%2F3994434&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmhTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=6b731fbb\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/120538/3994434</a>"},{"pid":"2f37611aee91824ccea5fa4f3dabaa56d4a10a22","tid":1480112,"uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:22:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/yxiLOeDCl9EUDTtmSHoZZg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9Njk2O2g9Mzk0/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/entertainment.nownews.hk/4b17c8acc35cf6366290b627792bedcb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FyxiLOeDCl9EUDTtmSHoZZg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9Njk2O2g9Mzk0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fentertainment.nownews.hk%2F4b17c8acc35cf6366290b627792bedcb&h=112c39cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39557dc2b7e24683eba1c2b23432e3251dc33bd7","tid":1480112,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:27:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/08/15/2073725-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F08%2F15%2F2073725-XXL.jpg&h=db442855&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dda4364f2116e92b1fb24d69882656ea0241edd7","tid":1480112,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:37:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a118167dae64d6a59e103a44888cd6dddbc6f84","tid":1480112,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:44:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FgbuDhY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFgbuDhY.gif&h=8708357c&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}